
---
// GlyphMate 1.0.2 changelog component
---


<article class="prose">
<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">GlyphMate 1.0.2</h3>
<div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">2025-10-05</div>


<h4 class="font-semibold mt-4">Added</h4>
<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
<li><strong>Security:</strong> Implemented a secure backend proxy using Firebase Cloud Functions to protect the Google Fonts API key.</li>
</ul>


<h4 class="font-semibold mt-4">Removed</h4>
<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
<li>Removed the `.env` file and the `flutter_dotenv` client dependency; API keys are no longer stored on the client.</li>
</ul>


<h4 class="font-semibold mt-4">Fixed</h4>
<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
<li>Resolved a networking issue in Windows release builds that prevented fetching Google Fonts.</li>
</ul>
</article>

